            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve the<strong> tomato paste</strong>,<strong> vegetable stock mix </strong>and<strong> chipotle paste</strong> (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) in 300ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[500ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your <strong>chipotle stock</strong></p><p>Gradually whisk the <strong>chipotle stock</strong> into the onions, a little at a time, and cook for 2-3 min (stirring occasionally) or until a smooth, thick sauce remains – this is your <strong>chipotle sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1682596191968-x200.jpg",
