            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chipotle sauce has thickened, transfer 1/3 to the measuring jug – this is your<strong> enchilada topping</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> drained black beans</strong>, <strong>cooked butternut squash & tomatoes</strong>,<strong> ground cumin </strong>and<strong> dried oregano</strong> to the remaining sauce in the pan and cook for a final 1-2 min or until thick – this is your <strong>butternut squash & black bean filling</strong></p><p>Grease an<strong> oven-proof dish </strong>with a little <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1682596202803-x200.jpg",
