            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide the <strong>butternut squash & black bean </strong>filling between the<strong> tortillas</strong>, roll each <strong>tortilla</strong> up and place them in the <strong>oven-proof dish</strong>, seam side down</p><p>Top with the<strong> enchilada topping </strong>(add a splash of water if needed to loosen to a spoonable consistency) and the<strong> grated cheeze</strong></p><p>Put the dish in the oven for 12-15 min or until the tortillas are crispy – these are your<strong> chipotle squash & bean enchiladas</strong></p>",
